'''欧洲压水反应堆'''（'''{{lang|en|EPR}}'''）是一种[[第三代反应堆|第三代]][[压水反应堆|压水反应堆]]（PWR）设计。它是被主要由在法国的"法玛通（Framatome）"（2011年至2017年間屬於[[阿海珐|阿海珐NP]]）和[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]（EDF）和德国[[西门子公司|西门子公司]]设计和开发的。在欧洲，这种反应堆的设计被称为'''欧洲压水反应堆'''，以及国际化的名称是'''进化动力反应堆'''(Evolutionary Power Reactor)，但是现在被[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]集团简单地命名为'''EPR'''。

目前有3台EPR的機組建造中、1台開始商業運轉，1部在芬蘭、1部在法國和2部在中國（广东省[[台山核电站|台山核电站]]2009與2010年動工）<ref>{{cite web|title=EDF hopes French EPR will launch before Chinese reactors|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/commoditiesNews/idAFL6N0Q665C20140731?sp=true|publisher=Reuters|author=Geert De Clercq|date=2014-07-31|accessdate=2014-12-09|archive-date=2014-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028054644/http://af.reuters.com/article/commoditiesNews/idAFL6N0Q665C20140731?sp=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>。目前芬蘭與法國建造中的EPR都遭遇了工期延宕的問題，中國台山核電廠的機組最初預定在2014、2015啟動聯網<ref>[http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Symbolic_milestone_for_Finnish_EPR-2410134.html Symbolic milestone for Finnish EPR] {{Wayback|url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Symbolic_milestone_for_Finnish_EPR-2410134.html |date=20190609090917 }}, ''World Nuclear News'', 24 October 2013.</ref>，台山1號機在2018年6月6日已啟動併網發電，2號機預定2019年啟動併網<ref name=wnn-20180102>{{cite news |url=http://world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Taishan-schedule-factors-in-commissioning-tests-0201181.html |title=Taishan schedule factors in commissioning tests |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2018-01-02 |accessdate=2018-01-03 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142023/http://world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Taishan-schedule-factors-in-commissioning-tests-0201181.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年9月，英国[[欣克利角C核电站|欣克利角]]核准興建2座EPR，预计将于2025年完成<ref name="guardian-20160915">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/sep/15/hinkley-point-c-nuclear-power-station-gets-go-ahead |title=Hinkley Point C nuclear power station gets government green light |author1=Rowena Mason |author2=Simon Goodley |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2016-09-15 |accessdate=2016-09-15 |archive-date=2016-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915162804/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2016/sep/15/hinkley-point-c-nuclear-power-station-gets-go-ahead |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]（EDF）承认在建设EPR设计方面的重大困难。2015年9月，[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]表示，“新型号”的EPR的设计正在进行中，这将更容易的和更便宜的建造<ref name="independent-20150923">{{cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/only-china-wants-to-invest-in-britains-new-2bn-hinkley-point-nuclear-plant-because-no-one-else-10513752.html |title=Only China wants to invest in Britain's new £2bn Hinkley Point nuclear station because no one else thinks it will work, EDF admits |author=Geert De Clercq |newspaper=The Independent |date=2015-09-23 |accessdate=2015-09-24 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924164054/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/only-china-wants-to-invest-in-britains-new-2bn-hinkley-point-nuclear-plant-because-no-one-else-10513752.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 设计 ==
EPR在國際上定位為[[第三代反應爐|第三代反應爐]]標準，採用[[壓水反應爐|壓水反應爐]]設計，反應爐基礎設計壽命60年，每2年更換一次燃料束。工程師計畫在提高反應爐安全性之餘，提升反應爐的電力輸出功率至1,650MW（热功率4500 MW），增加其商業競爭力。反應爐燃料棒可採用[[濃縮鈾|5％浓缩的铀氧化物]]、[[再處理鈾|再處理鈾]]或100％[[混合氧化物核燃料|混合氧化物核燃料]]。 

EPR是[[阿海珐|Framatome]] N4反應爐（輸出電力功率1,450MW）和[[西门子公司|西门子发电部门]]“Konvoi”反應爐（輸出電力功率1,290 - 1,400MW）兩種設計的改良進化型號<ref name="EPR-presentation">{{cite web |url=http://www.iaea.org/NuclearPower/Downloads/INPRO/Files/2010-Feb-DF-WS/15-Teller.pdf |format=PDF |title=The EPR Reactor: Evolution to Gen III+ based on proven technology |author=Andrew Teller |publisher=Areva |date=2010-02-02 |accessdate=2010-07-19 |archive-date=2012-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131220516/http://www.iaea.org/NuclearPower/Downloads/INPRO/Files/2010-Feb-DF-WS/15-Teller.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="EPR-brochure">{{cite web |url=http://www.areva-np.com/common/liblocal/docs/Brochure/EPR_US_%20May%202005.pdf |format=PDF |title=EPR – Areva brochure |publisher=Areva NP |date=May 2005 |accessdate=2008-01-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071129121411/http://www.areva-np.com/common/liblocal/docs/Brochure/EPR_US_%20May%202005.pdf |archivedate=2007-11-29 }}</ref>，工程師設計時希望它較[[第二代反应堆|第二代反应堆]]有高效率表現，EPR較前代反應爐每單位發電量運用的鈾燃料減少17%<ref>https://books.google.com/books?id=LZ7zBwWLyLEC&pg=PA121 page 126. 3 Rs of Nuclear Power: Reading, Recycling, and Reprocessing Making a Better ... By Jan Forsythe</ref>，因此可以更有效發揮鈾燃料棒的能量。不過西門子的核能工程部門在2011年解散，且西門子公司退出核子工業<ref name="DeutscheWelle1">{{cite web|last1=Borrud|first1=Gabriel|title=Siemens to quit nuclear industry|url=http://www.dw.com/en/siemens-to-quit-nuclear-industry/a-15396964|website=Deutsche Welle|accessdate=2016-10-11|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011161224/http://www.dw.com/en/siemens-to-quit-nuclear-industry/a-15396964|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 奥尔基洛托3号（芬兰） ==
[[File:OL3.jpg|thumb]]

芬兰奥尔基洛托3号（Olkiluoto 3）<ref>[http://www.ol3.areva-np.com/ OLKILUOTO 3 PROJECT by AREVA] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070210133742/http://www.ol3.areva-np.com/ |date=2007-02-10 }}</ref>电站的建设于2005年8月开始实施。它最初被计划在2009年上线<ref>[http://www.ol3.areva-np.com/project/chrono.htm CHRONOLOGY OF OLKILUOTO 3 PROJECT by AREVA] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927094543/http://www.ol3.areva-np.com/project/chrono.htm |date=2007-09-27 }}</ref>，但该项目已经遭受了许多延误，据[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]业务预计将于2018年才能开始运行<ref>{{cite news |title=Finland's Olkiluoto 3 reactor on track to start Dec 2018 -TVO executive |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/finland-nuclear-olkiluoto-idAFL8N1L34SS |accessdate=2021-10-22 |work=Reuters |date=2017-08-17 |language=en |archive-date=2021-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026022639/https://www.reuters.com/article/finland-nuclear-olkiluoto-idAFL8N1L34SS |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="wnn-01092014">{{cite news|url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Olkiluoto-3-start-up-pushed-back-to-2018-0109147.html|title=Olkiluoto 3 startup pushed back to 2018|date=2014-09-01|work=World Nuclear News|accessdate=2014-09-01|archive-date=2014-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904033804/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Olkiluoto-3-start-up-pushed-back-to-2018-0109147.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。该电站的电力输出功率为1600MW（净）。该建筑施工建造是法国[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]和德国[[西门子公司|西门子公司]]通过其芬兰运营商TVO的共同子公司Areva NP共同努力。西门子公司于2011年停止了核電業務。初步成本估计约为€37亿欧元<ref>[http://www.de.framatome-anp.com/anp/e/foa/anp/press/anp054.htm EPR IN FINLAND: FOUNDATION STONE-LAYING DAY AT OLKILUOTO 3 by AREVA] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061018024548/http://www.de.framatome-anp.com/anp/e/foa/anp/press/anp054.htm |date=2006-10-18 }}</ref>，但该项目已经出现了几个严重的成本增量和延迟。

{{As of|2009|5}}，该发电站至少延迟工期3年半，和超过预算的50％。[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]和电力公司卷入了争论“谁会承担成本超支，而现在电力公司将会违约是真正的风险”<ref name=tom>{{Cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/uk-expert--us-is-not-losing-international-race-on-nuclear-power-with-france-and-other-nations-61933312.html |title=U.K. Expert: U.S. is Not Losing International 'Race' on Nuclear Power With France and Other Nations |access-date=2018-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163022/https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/uk-expert--us-is-not-losing-international-race-on-nuclear-power-with-france-and-other-nations-61933312.html |archive-date=2018-06-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。 2009年8月，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]宣布为该项目增加€5.5亿欧元的资金，将电站成本增加到€53亿欧元，并在2009年上半年剔除了中期营运利润<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/0c9b59aa-9665-11de-84d1-00144feabdc0.html|title=Finnish reactor provisions hit Areva profits|author=Peggy Hollinger|date=2009-08-31|work=Financial Times|accessdate=2009-09-01|archive-date=2011-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901100226/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/0c9b59aa-9665-11de-84d1-00144feabdc0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年9月，安全壳结构的圆顶被封顶<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.areva.com/servlet/cp_ol3_06_09_2009-c-PressRelease-cid-1251741544566-en.html | title = Olkiluoto 3: EPR dome installed | publisher = AREVA NC | date=2009-08-06 | accessdate=2009-11-01}}</ref>。采购被完成90％，工程被完成80％，土建被完成73％<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJhyoZ8R4Ko | title=AREVA – Olkiluoto 3 : EPR dome installed | publisher=YouTube | date=2008-08-10 | accessdate=2009-11-29 | archive-date=2017-08-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170818024842/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oJhyoZ8R4Ko&feature=youtu.be | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年6月，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]宣布进一步拨备€4亿欧元，将成本超支至€27亿欧元。 2012年6月的时间尺度下滑至2012年底<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mineweb.co.za/mineweb/view/mineweb/en/page72103?oid=107035&sn=Detail&pid=102055 |title=S&P downgrades French nuclear-uranium giant AREVA on weakened profitability |author=Dorothy Kosich |publisher=Mineweb |date=2010-06-29 |accessdate=2010-07-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111004210130/http://www.mineweb.co.za/mineweb/view/mineweb/en/page72103?oid=107035&sn=Detail&pid=102055 |archivedate=2011-10-04 }}</ref><ref name=fb>François de Beaupuy. [http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-06-24/areva-s-overruns-at-finnish-nuclear-plant-approach-initial-cost.html Areva’s Overruns at Finnish Nuclear Plant Approach Initial Cost] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100907020504/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-06-24/areva-s-overruns-at-finnish-nuclear-plant-approach-initial-cost.html |date=7 September 2010 }} ''Bloomberg Businessweek'', 24 June 2010.</ref>，阿海珐在芬兰核电站进行初始成本超支，预计将于2013年启动<ref name="wnn-20100608">{{cite news |title=Start-up of Finnish EPR pushed back to 2013 |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2010-06-08 |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Startup_of_Finnish_EPR_pushed_back_to_2013-0806104.html |accessdate=2010-06-28 |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618230207/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Startup_of_Finnish_EPR_pushed_back_to_2013-0806104.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2011年12月，TVO宣布将延期至2014年8月<ref name="reuters-20111221">{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/21/finland-olkiluoto-idUSL6E7NL2DI20111221 |title=Finland's Olkiluoto 3 reactor delayed to August 2014 |publisher=Reuters |date=2011-12-21 |accessdate=2011-12-21 |first=Ritsuko |last=Ando |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924161205/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/12/21/finland-olkiluoto-idUSL6E7NL2DI20111221 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 截至2012年7月，该电站计划在2015年之前开始发电，计划已经延迟至少6年<ref name = "world-nuclear-news20120716">{{cite news | title = Olkiluoto 3 delayed beyond 2014 | publisher = World Nuclear News | date = 2012-07-17 | url = http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Olkiluoto_3_delayed_beyond_2014-1707124.html | accessdate = 2012-07-31 | archive-date = 2017-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171024095911/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Olkiluoto_3_delayed_beyond_2014-1707124.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。 2012年12月，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]的首席执行官估计成本为€80亿欧元<ref>{{cite news | title = Costs of Finland's Olkiluoto nuclear reactor go up yet again | publisher = Nuclear-news | date = 2012-12-14 | url = http://nuclear-news.net/2012/12/14/costs-of-finlands-olkiluoto-nuclear-reactor-go-up-yet-again/ | accessdate = 2013-09-06 | archive-date = 2018-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180618125606/https://nuclear-news.net/2012/12/14/costs-of-finlands-olkiluoto-nuclear-reactor-go-up-yet-again/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2014年9月，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]宣布将于2018年开始运营<ref name="wnn-01092014" />。 在2017年10月，这个日期被推到2019年初<ref>{{Cite News|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-10-09/finland-s-10-year-wait-for-a-new-nuclear-reactor-just-got-longer|title=Finland’s 10-Year Wait for a Nuclear Reactor Just Got Longer|publisher=Bloomberg|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010211648/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-10-09/finland-s-10-year-wait-for-a-new-nuclear-reactor-just-got-longer|archive-date=2017-10-10|dead-url=no|date= 2017-10-09|access-date = 2017-10-10}}</ref>, 和由于测试延误，在2018年6月发电日期又被推到2019年9月<ref name=wnn-20180614>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Start-up-of-Finnish-EPR-put-back-four-months-1406184.html |title=Start-up of Finnish EPR put back four months |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2018-06-14 |accessdate=2018-06-15 |archive-date=2019-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403200405/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Start-up-of-Finnish-EPR-put-back-four-months-1406184.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2018年11月宣布进一步延迟４个月：常规发电将于2020年1月开始<ref name=wnn-20181129>{{cite news |url=http://world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/New-delay-in-start-up-of-Finnish-EPR |title=New delay in start-up of Finnish EPR |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2018-11-29 |accessdate=2018-12-03 |archive-date=2019-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423155341/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/New-delay-in-start-up-of-Finnish-EPR |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 弗拉芒维尔3号（法国） ==
{{See also|法国核能}}
[[File:Flamanville-3_2010-07-15.jpg|thumb]]

2007年12月6日，在{{le|弗拉芒维尔核电站|Flamanville Nuclear Power Plant}}(Flamanville)为第一个混凝土浇筑了示范性的EPR反应堆<ref>''Nuclear Engineering International''. [http://www.neimagazine.com/story.asp?sectionCode=132&storyCode=2048041 Flamanville 3 concrete poured] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110613091002/http://www.neimagazine.com/story.asp?sectionCode=132&storyCode=2048041 |date=2011-06-13 }}.</ref>。顾名思义，这将是弗拉芒维尔核电站的第三个核反应堆，和正在建造的EPR的第二个反应堆。电力产量将为1630 MW（净），该项目计划涉及法国电力公司约€33亿欧元的资本支出<ref name=EDF>{{cite web |url=http://www.edf.fr/html/epr/uk/projet.html |title=EDF Official Site – Flamanville 3 |publisher=Edf.fr |accessdate=2012-04-19 |archive-date=2009-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090630101014/http://energy.edf.com/edf-fr-accueil/edf-and-power-generation/nuclear-power/the-future-of-nuclear-power/epr-y-flamanville-3/the-flamanville-3-project-122321.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

从2005年10月19日至2006年2月18日，该项目已提交国家公开辩论。 2006年5月4日，法国电力公司董事会决定继续进行施工。 在2006年6月15日至7月31日期间，该部门接受了公众调查，对该项目给予了“赞成意见”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://construction.ecnext.com/coms2/summary_0249-218321_ITM_platts |title=Public inquiry commission favours plan to build Flamanville-3 EPR |date=2006-10-05 |work=Nucleonics Week |accessdate=2008-06-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929135733/http://construction.ecnext.com/coms2/summary_0249-218321_ITM_platts |archivedate=2007-09-29 |subscription=yes}}</ref>。 在那个夏天，场地准备工作开始了。

2007年12月该单位本身开始建设。 预计建设将持续54个月。

2008年4月，[[法國原子能安全委員會|法國原子能安全委員會]]（Autorité de sûreté nucléaire，缩写：ASN）报告说，二次安全壳钢衬里检查的焊缝中有四分之一与规范不符，并且在混凝土基层发现了裂缝。 [[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]表示，在建设初期提出的这些问题正在取得进展<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/defects-found-in-nuclear-reactor-the-french-want-to-build-in-britain-808461.html |title=Defects found in nuclear reactor the French want to build in Britain |author1=Geoffrey Lean |author2=Jonathan Owen |date=2008-04-13 |work=The Independent |accessdate=2004-04-19 |location=London |archive-date=2017-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821214531/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/defects-found-in-nuclear-reactor-the-french-want-to-build-in-britain-808461.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>;然而，5月21日，[[法國原子能安全委員會|法國原子能安全委員會]]下令暂停混凝土浇筑<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/rbssIndustryMaterialsUtilitiesNews/idUSL2762459720080527 |title=French nuke body partly halts work on new reactor |date=2008-05-27 |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2008-05-27 |archive-date=2021-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604055801/https://www.reuters.com/article/rbssIndustryMaterialsUtilitiesNews/idUSL2762459720080527 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 一个月后，[[法國原子能安全委員會|法國原子能安全委員會]]接受了[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]的纠正措施计划，其中包括外部监督检查后恢复了混凝土工作<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS_EdF_allowed_to_continue_concreting_2006081.html |title=EdF allowed to continue concreting |date=2008-06-20 |publisher=World Nuclear News |accessdate=2008-06-21 |archive-date=2017-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812101305/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS_EdF_allowed_to_continue_concreting_2006081.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年5月，Stephen Thomas教授报告说，经过18个月的建设并经过一系列质量控制问题后，该项目“超过预算20％以上，EDF正在着挣扎保持按计划进行。<ref name="tom"/>”

2010年8月，监管机构[[法國原子能安全委員會|法國原子能安全委員會]]（ASN）报告了二次密封钢衬垫上的进一步焊接问题<ref name="bloomberg-20100830" />。 同一个月，[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]宣布成本增加50％，达到€50亿欧元，并且到2014年，调试延迟了大约2年<ref name="bloomberg-20100830">{{cite news |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-30/edf-has-welding-problems-at-flamanville-epr-reactor-french-watchdog-says.html |title=French Nuclear Watchdog Says EDF Has Problems With Flamanville EPR Liner |author=Tara Patel |publisher=[[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]] |date=2010-08-30 |accessdate=2010-08-31 |archive-date=2012-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121103131942/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-30/edf-has-welding-problems-at-flamanville-epr-reactor-french-watchdog-says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年7月，[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]宣布估计成本已上升至€60亿欧元，并且施工完成延迟至2016年<ref name=neimagazine>
{{Cite news | url= http://www.neimagazine.com/story.asp?sectioncode=132&storyCode=2060192 | agency= Nuclear Engineering International | date= 2011-07-20 | title= EDF delays Flamanville 3 EPR project | accessdate= 2011-07-21 | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20120319191541/http://www.neimagazine.com/story.asp?sectioncode=132&storyCode=2060192 | archivedate= 2012年3月19日 }}</ref>
。

2012年12月3日，[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]宣布估计成本已上升至€85亿欧元<ref name=lemonde>{{Cite news | url=http://www.lemonde.fr/planete/article/2012/12/03/le-cout-de-l-epr-de-flamanville-encore-revu-a-la-hausse_1799417_3244.html | agency=Le Monde | date=2012-12-03 | title=Le coût de l'EPR de Flamanville encore revu à la hausse | accessdate=2012-12-04 | archive-date=2018-01-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118191051/http://www.lemonde.fr/planete/article/2012/12/03/le-cout-de-l-epr-de-flamanville-encore-revu-a-la-hausse_1799417_3244.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年11月，[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]宣布，由于延迟了[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]组件的交付，因此完工将延期至2017年<ref name="ft-20141118">{{cite news |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/adc90b3e-6f67-11e4-8d86-00144feabdc0.html |title=EDF in fresh delay for flagship nuclear plant |author=Michael Stothard |newspaper=Financial Times |date=2014-11-18 |accessdate=2014-11-21 |archive-date=2016-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325031356/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/adc90b3e-6f67-11e4-8d86-00144feabdc0.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年4月，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]向法国核监管机构[[法國原子能安全委員會|ASN]]通报，反应堆容器钢中发现异常，导致“机械韧性值低于预期值”。 进一步的测试正在进行中<ref name="wnn-20150407">{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-Flamanville-EPR-vessel-anomalies-under-scrutiny-0704154.html |title=Flamanville EPR vessel anomalies under scrutiny |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2015-04-07 |accessdate=2015-04-11 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304053730/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-Flamanville-EPR-vessel-anomalies-under-scrutiny-0704154.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2015年7月，《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》报道，自2006年以来，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]一直意识到这个问题<ref name="telegraph-20150709">{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/earth/energy/nuclearpower/11727000/Areva-aware-as-early-as-2006-of-serious-fault-in-nuclear-reactor-destined-for-UK.html |title=Areva aware 'as early as 2006' of serious fault in nuclear reactor destined for UK |author=Henry Samuel |newspaper=Daily Telegraph |date=2015-07-09 |accessdate=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613230542/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/earth/energy/nuclearpower/11727000/Areva-aware-as-early-as-2006-of-serious-fault-in-nuclear-reactor-destined-for-UK.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2015年6月，[[法國原子能安全委員會|ASN]]发现了冷却系统安全阀的多处故障<ref name="telegraph-20150609">{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11662889/Faulty-valves-in-new-generation-EPR-nuclear-reactor-pose-meltdown-risk-inspectors-warn.html |title=Faulty valves in new-generation EPR nuclear reactor pose meltdown risk, inspectors warn |author=Henry Samuel |newspaper=Daily Telegraph |date=2015-06-09 |accessdate=2015-07-09 |archive-date=2018-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614005419/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/france/11662889/Faulty-valves-in-new-generation-EPR-nuclear-reactor-pose-meltdown-risk-inspectors-warn.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年9月，法国电力公司宣布估计成本已上升至€105亿欧元，反应堆启动时间推迟至2018年第4季度<ref name="EDF-timetable">https://www.edf.fr/en/edf/press_release/Flamanville-EPR-optimised-project-management-and-a-new-timetable</ref>。

2016年4月，[[法國原子能安全委員會|ASN]]宣布在反应堆钢中发现了其他薄弱环节，阿海珐和法国电力公司回应称将进行新的测试，但建筑工程将继续进行<ref name="nei-20160412">{{cite news |url=https://www.neimagazine.com/news/newseprs-to-face-more-tests-4862270 |title=EPRs to face more tests |publisher=Nuclear Engineering International |date=2016-04-12 |accessdate=2016-04-13 |archive-date=2019-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403092235/https://www.neimagazine.com/news/newseprs-to-face-more-tests-4862270 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年2月，英国《[[金融时报_(英国)|金融时报]]》称该项目延迟6年，超出预算72亿欧元<ref name=ft-20170214>{{cite news |url=https://www.ft.com/content/416a2c9c-f2d3-11e6-8758-6876151821a6 |title=Downfall of Toshiba, a nuclear industry titan |newspaper=Financial Times |date=2017-02-14 |accessdate=2017-02-15 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414175636/https://www.ft.com/content/416a2c9c-f2d3-11e6-8758-6876151821a6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[台山核电站|台山核电站]]EPR反应堆建设的延迟再次促使法国电力公司表示Flamanville 3仍按计划启动, 假设获得监管机构的批准，到2018年底开始运营<ref>{{cite news |url= http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/edf-confirms-flamanville-timetable-after-taishan-epr-delay/articleshow/57294950.cms |title= EDF confirms Flamanville timetable after Taishan EPR delay |work= [[Times_of_India|Times of India]] |date= 2017-02-22 |accessdate= 2017-03-09 |archive-date= 2017-02-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170226100903/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/international-business/edf-confirms-flamanville-timetable-after-taishan-epr-delay/articleshow/57294950.cms |dead-url= no }}</ref>。 2017年6月，法国监管机构发布了一项临时裁决，Flamanville 3可以安全启动<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-French-regulator-says-Flamanville-3-is-safe-to-start-29061701.html |title= French regulator says Flamanville 3 is safe to start |publisher= World Nuclear News |date= 2017-06-28 |accessdate= 2017-07-03 |archive-date= 2019-06-01 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190601001646/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-French-regulator-says-Flamanville-3-is-safe-to-start-29061701.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

焊接质量偏差的发现导致2018年7月的进度计划进一步修订。燃料装载延迟到2019年底（最早在2020年开始定期发电），成本从€105亿欧元增加至109亿欧元<ref name="Flamanville-timetable">{{cite news |url= http://world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/EDF-revises-schedule,-costs-of-Flamanville-EPR |title= EDF revises schedule, costs of Flamanville EPR |publisher= World Nuclear News |date= 2018-07-25 |accessdate= 2018-07-30 |archive-date= 2019-04-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190423152632/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/EDF-revises-schedule,-costs-of-Flamanville-EPR |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

== 台山1号和2号（中国） ==
{{See also|中华人民共和国核工业|台山核电站}}
2006年，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]与[[东芝|东芝]]拥有的[[西屋公司|西屋公司]]（Westinghouse）和[[俄罗斯原子能出口公司|俄罗斯原子能出口公司]](Atomstroyexport)一起参加了在中国建造四座新核反应堆的首个招标过程<ref>{{cite web |author=english@peopledaily.com.cn |url=http://english.people.com.cn/200409/12/eng20040912_156691.html |title=Foreign energy giants bid for China's nuclear contracts, 12 September 2004, ''People's Daily'' |work=People's Daily |date=2004-09-12 |accessdate=2012-04-19 |archive-date=2012-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204035841/http://english.people.com.cn/200409/12/eng20040912_156691.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，由于[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]拒绝将专业知识和知识转移给中国，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]因此失去了对西屋[[AP1000|AP1000]]反应堆的投标{{Citation needed|date=November 2015}}。

尽管坚持了以往的条件，[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]依然在2007年2月成功获得了一笔交易——两座位于中国南方[[广东省|广东省]][[台山市|台山]]的欧洲压水反应堆价值约为80亿欧元（约合105亿美元）。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/newsarticle.aspx?id=14454&LangType=2057 |title=Areva lands world's biggest ever nuclear power order |date=2007-11-26 |work=World Nuclear News |accessdate=2013-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130413014154/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/newsarticle.aspx?id=14454&LangType=2057 |archive-date=2013-04-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/business/feeds/afx/2007/07/30/afx3965097.html |title=Signing of Areva EPR order in China delayed – French source |date=2007-07-30 |work=Forbes |accessdate=2007-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215151621/http://www.forbes.com/business/feeds/afx/2007/07/30/afx3965097.html |archivedate=2008-12-15 }}</ref>。[[承建商|承建商]]和运营商是[[中国广核集团|中国广核集团]]（CGN）。

[[台山核电站|台山]]1号反应堆的建设工作于2009年11月18日正式启动，2号反应堆的建设工作于2010年4月15日正式启动<ref name="IAEA-PRIS-china">{{cite web |title=China, People's Republic of: Nuclear Power Reactors |url=http://www.iaea.org/cgi-bin/db.page.pl/pris.powrea.htm?country=CN |work=PRIS database |publisher=[[International_Atomic_Energy_Agency|International Atomic Energy Agency]] (IAEA) |accessdate=2010-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620074942/http://www.iaea.org/cgi-bin/db.page.pl/pris.powrea.htm?country=CN |archivedate=2010-06-20 }}</ref>。 然后计划每个单元机组的建设需要46个月，显著比芬兰和法国的前两个欧洲压水反应堆更快速，和更便宜<ref>{{cite news | url= https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-24/china-builds-french-designed-nuclear-reactor-for-40-less-areva-ceo-says.html | title= China Builds Nuclear Reactor for 40% Less Than Cost in France, Areva Says | first= Tara | last= Patel | author2= François de Beaupuy | date= 2010-11-24 | publisher= [[Bloomberg_L.P.|Bloomberg]] | accessdate= 2010-12-02 | archive-date= 2015-01-08 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150108010442/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-24/china-builds-french-designed-nuclear-reactor-for-40-less-areva-ceo-says.html | dead-url= no }}</ref>。

1号反应堆的反应堆[[反應爐壓力槽|反應爐壓力槽]]于2012年6月安装<ref>{{cite news | url= http://www.areva.com/EN/news-9361/china-the-construction-of-the-epr-reactor-unit-1-at-taishan-takes-a-major-step-forward-with-the-installation-of-the-vessel.html | title= China: The Construction of the EPR reactor Unit 1 at Taishan Takes a Major Step Forward with the Installation of the Vessel | date= 2012-06-05 | publisher= [[AREVA|AREVA]] | accessdate= 2012-06-05 | archive-date= 2017-07-07 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170707114031/http://www.areva.com/EN/news-9361/china-the-construction-of-the-epr-reactor-unit-1-at-taishan-takes-a-major-step-forward-with-the-installation-of-the-vessel.html | dead-url= no }}</ref>，第二台在2014年11月安装。台山1号压力容器由日本[[三菱重工业|三菱重工业]]进口，法国[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]的蒸汽发生器。 第二个压力容器和相关的蒸汽发生器是由中国的[[东方电气|东方电气]]和[[上海电气|上海电气]]公司制造的<ref name="wnn-20141105">{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Construction-milestone-at-Taishan-2-EPR-0511141.html |title=Construction milestone at Taishan 2 EPR |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2014-11-05 |accessdate=2016-04-13 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613160329/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Construction-milestone-at-Taishan-2-EPR-0511141.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

据报道，2014年的建设延迟了两年，主要原因是关键部件延误和项目管理问题<ref name="nei-20150223">{{cite news |url=http://www.neimagazine.com/opinion/opinionhow-serious-are-the-delays-in-chinas-nuclear-programme-4517469/ |title=How serious are the delays in China's nuclear programme? |author=Steve Kidd |publisher=Nuclear Engineering International |date=2015-02-23 |accessdate=2015-03-08 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402133810/http://www.neimagazine.com/opinion/opinionhow-serious-are-the-delays-in-chinas-nuclear-programme-4517469/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

于2016年2月在台山1号进行了冷功能测试，预计2017年上半年启动。台山2号计划于当年晚些时候启动<ref name="wnn-20160201">{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-First-Taishan-EPR-completes-cold-tests-0102164.html |title=First Taishan EPR completes cold tests |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2016-02-01 |accessdate=2016-04-13 |archive-date=2017-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222105019/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-First-Taishan-EPR-completes-cold-tests-0102164.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 然而，投产日期已于2017年2月延迟六个月，预计将于2017年下半年和2018年上半年投入商业运营<ref name=wnn-20170222>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-China-revises-commissioning-dates-of-EPRs-2202174.html |title=China revises commissioning dates of EPRs |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2017-02-22 |accessdate=2017-02-25 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612141213/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-China-revises-commissioning-dates-of-EPRs-2202174.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年12月，香港媒体报道，一个组件在测试过程中破裂，需要更换<ref name="crackinkey">{{cite news |title=香港个股：中广核电力称台山核电站除氧器更换接近结束，建设稳妥推进 |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AA%E8%82%A1%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%BF%E6%A0%B8%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%A7%B0%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%B1%E6%A0%B8%E7%94%B5%E7%AB%99%E9%99%A4%E6%B0%A7%E5%99%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%A8%B3%E5%A6%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9B-idCNL3S1OC2R0 |accessdate=2021-10-22 |work=Reuters |date=2017-12-12 |language=en |archive-date=2021-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211022060348/https://www.reuters.com/article/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AA%E8%82%A1%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%BF%E6%A0%B8%E7%94%B5%E5%8A%9B%E7%A7%B0%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%B1%E6%A0%B8%E7%94%B5%E7%AB%99%E9%99%A4%E6%B0%A7%E5%99%A8%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2%E6%8E%A5%E8%BF%91%E7%BB%93%E6%9D%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E7%A8%B3%E5%A6%A5%E6%8E%A8%E8%BF%9B-idCNL3S1OC2R0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年1月调试再次重新安排，预计2018年和2019年商业运营<ref name="wnn-20180102"/>。

2018年6月6日，台山1号首次达到[[臨界|臨界]]状态<ref name=wnn-20180607 />。2018年6月29日并网发电。2018年12月13日商业运营<ref name=wnn-20181214 /><ref>{{cite web |title=Bernard Fontana's statement - EPR: the first Generation III+ nuclear reactor enters commercial operation |url=http://www.framatome.com/EN/businessnews-1445/nbspbernard-fontana-s-statement-epr-the-first-generation-iii-nuclear-reactor-enters-commercial-operation.html |publisher=Framatome |date=2018-12-14 |accessdate=2018-12-16 |archive-date=2019-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604160509/http://www.framatome.com/EN/businessnews-1445/nbspbernard-fontana-s-statement-epr-the-first-generation-iii-nuclear-reactor-enters-commercial-operation.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 台山核电站二号机组2019年9月7日商业运营。

== 欣克利角C（英国）==
{{see also|欣克利角C核电站}}
EPR与西屋[[AP1000|AP1000]]一起进行了核管理办公室通用设计评估<ref>{{cite web|title=New Nuclear Power Stations – Progress so far|url=http://www.hse.gov.uk/newreactors/progress.htm|publisher=[[Health_and_Safety_Executive|Health and Safety Executive]]|accessdate=2009-09-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601205003/http://www.hse.gov.uk/newreactors/progress.htm|archivedate=2009-06-01}}</ref>。临时设计验收确认已被推迟，直至[[福岛第一核电站事故|福岛第一核电站事故]]的教训被考虑到<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hse.gov.uk/newreactors/gda-japan.htm |title=News – Taking GDA work forward in the light of the unprecedented events in Japan |publisher=Hse.gov.uk |accessdate=2012-04-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111228221748/http://www.hse.gov.uk/newreactors/gda-japan.htm |archivedate=2011-12-28 }}</ref>。EDF在2009年购买了“英国能源”。EDF计划在4个新的EPR<ref>{{cite web |author=This website was built by the EDF Energy WCM |url=http://www.edfenergy.com/about-us/energy-generation/nuclear.shtml |title=Nuclear Generation |publisher=Edfenergy.com |accessdate=2012-04-19 |archive-date=2011-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110412211815/http://www.edfenergy.com/about-us/energy-generation/nuclear.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>的基础上，与政府达成电价协议<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nce.co.uk/news/energy/edf-still-undecided-about-hinkley-point-c-go-ahead/8646617.article?blocktitle=Exclusive-news-from-NCE-magazine&contentID=204 |title=EdF still undecided about Hinkley Point C go-ahead |author=Declan Lynch |newspaper=New Civil Engineer |date=2013-04-18 |accessdate=2013-04-21 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081302/http://www.nce.co.uk/news/energy/edf-still-undecided-about-hinkley-point-c-go-ahead/8646617.article?blocktitle=Exclusive-news-from-NCE-magazine&contentID=204 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="telegraph-20130418">{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/energy/10004699/EDF-prepared-to-let-UK-nuclear-talks-fail.html |title=EDF prepared to let UK nuclear talks fail |author=Andrew Trotman |newspaper=Daily Telegraph |date=2013-04-18 |accessdate=2013-04-21 |archive-date=2013-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421000512/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/newsbysector/energy/10004699/EDF-prepared-to-let-UK-nuclear-talks-fail.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]已经与[[罗尔斯·罗伊斯股份有限公司|罗尔斯·罗伊斯股份有限公司]]签署了战略合作伙伴关系，以支持EPR的建设<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.neimagazine.com/story.asp?storyCode=2059128 |title=Areva signs up Rolls-Royce for EPR |publisher=Nuclear Engineering International |date=2011-03-11 |accessdate=2012-04-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120319191429/http://www.neimagazine.com/story.asp?storyCode=2059128 |archivedate=2012-03-19 }}</ref>。2013年3月19日，[[欣克利角C核电站|欣克利角C核电站]]的规划同意已经被给出<ref name="bbc-20130320">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-21839684 |title=New nuclear power plant at Hinkley Point C is approved |publisher=BBC |date=2013-03-20 |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160916203304/http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-21839684 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但是与英国政府就电价和与私人投资者进行项目融资的困难谈判仍有待完成<ref name="bbc-20130319">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-somerset-21774652 |title=What price nuclear power? The final hurdle for Hinkley |author=Dave Harvey |publisher=BBC |date=2013-03-19 |accessdate=2013-03-19 |archive-date=2013-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130322180405/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-somerset-21774652 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

于2013年10月21日，[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]宣布就欣克利角C厂址兴建的核电站达成协议。英国政府就投资合约的主要商业条款达成一致。 最终的投资决定取决于完成其余关键步骤，包括[[欧洲联盟委员会|欧洲联盟委员会]]的协议。

2016年7月28日，在一名董事会成员辞职后，[[法国电力公司|法国电力公司]]董事会批准了该项目<ref name="guardian-20160728">{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/jul/28/hinkley-point-c-to-go-ahead-after-edf-board-approves-project |title=Hinkley Point C in doubt after British government delays approval |author=Graham Ruddick |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2016-07-28 |accessdate=2016-07-30 |archive-date=2016-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729162618/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/jul/28/hinkley-point-c-to-go-ahead-after-edf-board-approves-project |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 然而，[[第一次文翠珊內閣|第一次文翠珊內閣]]新政府新任商务，能源和工业战略大臣[[格雷格·克拉克|格雷格·克拉克]]随后宣布政府不会按照预期在未来几天签署合同，但将合同延迟到秋季"仔细考虑这个项目的所有组成部分"<ref name="telegraph-20160728">{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2016/07/28/green-light-for-hinkley-point-as-new-18bn-nuclear-plant-approved/ |title=Government delays Hinkley nuclear decision despite EDF approval for £18bn project |author=Emily Gosden |newspaper=Daily Telegraph |date=2016-07-28 |accessdate=2016-07-28 |archive-date=2016-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803062819/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2016/07/28/green-light-for-hinkley-point-as-new-18bn-nuclear-plant-approved/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 最终政府批准于2016年9月<ref name="guardian-20160915" />。
2017年7月，经过内部审查，法国电力公司宣布了对该计划的修订估算，其中包括至少£1.5亿英镑的额外费用和最多15个月的额外计划，导致最新的总成本估算为£196-203亿英镑（€220-228亿欧元）<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.ft.com/content/d4333820-5fcf-11e7-8814-0ac7eb84e5f1?mhq5j=e1 |title= EDF warns Hinkley Point could cost extra £1.5bn |work= [[Financial_Times|Financial Times]] |date= 2017-07-03 |accessdate= 2017-07-05 |archive-date= 2017-09-10 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170910142912/https://www.ft.com/content/d4333820-5fcf-11e7-8814-0ac7eb84e5f1?mhq5j=e1 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.globalconstructionreview.com/news/hinkley-nuclear-plant-already-15bn-over-budget-edf/ |title= Hinkley nuclear plant already £1.5bn over budget, EDF admits |work= Global Construction Review |date= 2017-07-03 |accessdate= 2017-07-05 |archive-date= 2017-07-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170705140825/http://www.globalconstructionreview.com/news/hinkley-nuclear-plant-already-15bn-over-budget-edf/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2017/07/03/hinkley-nuclear-costs-climb-almost-20bn-start-delayed/|title=Cost of Hinkley Point nuclear plant climbs another £1.5bn to over £20bn, as project faces further delay|last=Ambrose|first=Jillian|date=2017-07-03|work=The Telegraph|access-date=2018-09-17|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2018-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180917182015/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2017/07/03/hinkley-nuclear-costs-climb-almost-20bn-start-delayed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==未来可能的发电站==

===印度===
2009年2月，{{le|印度核电公司|Nuclear Power Corporation of India}}（NPCIL）与[[阿海珐|阿海珐]]签署了一份谅解备忘录，在马哈拉施特拉邦的Jaitapur建立了两座1650 WM的反应堆。随后于2010年12月签署了框架协议<ref>[http://www.npcil.nic.in//pdf/news_07dec2010_Business_Line.pdf India, France ink pact for Areva reactors, fuel] {{Wayback|url=http://www.npcil.nic.in//pdf/news_07dec2010_Business_Line.pdf |date=20110927225957 }} npcil.nic.in</ref>。

2016年1月，在法国总统[[弗朗索瓦·奥朗德|弗朗索瓦·奥朗德]]对印度进行国事访问期间，印度总理[[纳伦德拉·莫迪|纳伦德拉·莫迪]]发表了联合声明。根据声明，两位领导人“已商定合作路线图，以加快2016年Jaitapur项目的讨论。他们的共同目标是在2017年初开始实施该项目。”<ref name="wnn-201690125">{{cite news |url=http://world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Jaitapur-agreement-due-by-year-end-2501165.html |title=Jaitapur agreement due by year-end |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2016-01-25 |accessdate=2016-05-19 |archive-date=2019-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190606143921/http://world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Jaitapur-agreement-due-by-year-end-2501165.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年3月10日，EDF与NPCIL签署了工业路向协议(Industrial Way Forward Agreement)，目标是在今年晚些时候进行招标<ref name=wnn-20180312>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Way-forward-agreed-for-Jaitapur-reactors-1203187.html |title=Way forward agreed for Jaitapur reactors |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2018-03-12 |accessdate=2018-06-27 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609130428/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Way-forward-agreed-for-Jaitapur-reactors-1203187.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=wnn-20180627>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-EDF-and-GE-sign-strategic-deal-for-six-EPRs-in-India-26061802.html |title=EDF and GE sign strategic deal for six EPRs in India |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2018-06-27 |accessdate=2018-06-27 |archive-date=2019-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423144203/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-EDF-and-GE-sign-strategic-deal-for-six-EPRs-in-India-26061802.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

NPCIL有望在Jaitapur工厂建造高达9900兆瓦的电力，相当于6个EPR<ref name="wnn-20150413">{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Areva-signs-Jaitapur-agreements-1304154.html |title=Areva signs Jaitapur agreements |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2015-04-13 |accessdate=2015-04-14 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608121003/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/NN-Areva-signs-Jaitapur-agreements-1304154.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===英国===

位于英国Sizewell的两个EPR单位正处于规划的早期阶段<ref name=wnn-20180118>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/EDF-Energy-expects-20-cost-saving-for-Sizewell-C |title=EDF Energy expects 20% cost saving for Sizewell C |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=2018-01-18 |accessdate=2018-08-14 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609130430/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/Articles/EDF-Energy-expects-20-cost-saving-for-Sizewell-C |dead-url=no }}</ref>。如果项目继续进行，预计电力生产最早将于2031年开始<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gosden|first1=Emily|title=Sizewell C nuclear power to come on stream in 2031|work=The Times|issue=72367|date=2017-10-20|page=42|issn=0140-0460}}</ref>。

